

//Original Code to print "Hello, World":





public class Hello{
public static void main(String args[]){
Sydtem.out.println("Hello,World");
}
}













---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Case1- When class name is different from file name:

File name Hello.java
Class name HelloWorld

Compile time error.
Hello.java:1: error: class HelloWorld is public, should be declared in a file named HelloWorld.java
public class  HelloWorld


----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------



Case2- When main function is missing:

Compiled Successfully.
Error: Main method not found in class Hello, please define the main method as:
   public static void main(String[] args)
or a JavaFX application class must extend javafx.application.Application


------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


Case3- Delete .class file and then run the program:


Error: Could not find or load main class Hello


----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


